column5: went up to mountsberg i got a smallie lots of small perch this perch and my buddy got a hammerhandle
Great report. Sounds like a day well spent. Thanks for sharing.
How are the weeds and water level johnl?
the water levels are pretty high because of that rain we were fishing from shore so i cant really give an accurate account of the weeds and im 90 percent sure it was a smallie
Sounds like a fun day out.
